extendedInfo.description: The Sea Dragon is the defender of the open seas from the ancient times.In appearance filled with affection,cures and heals each soul to the path of one."Dream Monday Family" can also use the wallpapers of this app.We recommend "Dream Monday Family" to the customer who purchased some our live wallpapers and want to use many wallpaper.https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dmf.wall.DMFLwpSub*To use:Menu>Wallpapers>LiveWallpapers->Sea Dragon Aqua*Portrait only.*Please try the free version first.https://market.android.com/details?id=com.dmf.wall.SeaDragonAquaFree*The scrolling depends behavior of Home application.If scrolling does not work or something strange, try to check Home app's settings.(scrolling speed, overshoot, etc.)*Please resetting if the screen turn black when updating it with setting the wallpaper.
